<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset and Base Styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* Navbar Styles */
        .navbar {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1d3557, #457b9d);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .navbar .logo {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .navbar a {
            color: white;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }
        .navbar a:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #457b9d, #1d3557);
            color: white;
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 50px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 50px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #1d3557;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #1d3557;
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* About Section */
        .about {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }
        .about h2 {
            color: #1d3557;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .about p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 10px;
        }

        /* Values Section */
        .values {
            padding: 60px 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        .values h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #457b9d;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .value-cards {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .value-card {
            background: #f4f4f4;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            max-width: 280px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .value-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .value-card h3 {
            color: #1d3557;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1d3557, #457b9d);
            color: white;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #f4a261;
            text-decoration: underline;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            color: #e76f51;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.4rem;
            }
            .hero p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
            .values .value-cards {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <div class="logo">About Us</div>
        <div>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Discover Our Journey</h1>
        <p>Driven by passion, innovation, and a commitment to excellence.</p>
        <a href="#our-mission" class="btn-primary">Explore More</a>
    </section>

    <section id="our-mission" class="about">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>We are a team of dedicated professionals united by a vision to deliver transformative solutions. Through collaboration and creativity, we aim to empower individuals and businesses worldwide.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="our-values" class="values">
        <h2>What We Stand For</h2>
        <div class="value-cards">
            <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Customer Focus</h3>
                <p>Everything we do is centered on providing value to our customers.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Innovation</h3>
                <p>We thrive on pushing boundaries and finding new ways to solve challenges.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Integrity</h3>
                <p>We uphold transparency, trust, and honesty in every interaction.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 About Us. <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
